en_218445_0	Brigadier P. A. D Kahapola, Director, Human Rights & Humanitarian Law (HR & HL) of the Gemunu Watch Regiment passed away on Friday (1) following a brief illness at Piliyandala Hospital.
en_218445_1	His remains are now lying at his residence, No 210/4/D, Horana Road, Piliyandala.
en_218445_2	His funeral with Military honors takes place on Monday (4) at Pubudu Play Ground in Kahapola at 4.00 p.m.
